snippet.title: Chinese Love Songs
snippet.description:
Fan-made music video trailer taken scenes from Chinese & Korean movies and television drama series.  The song in the video is either from its soundtrack or various popular, classic and latest Chinese & Korean sentimental love songs to fit best for that theme video.

I enjoy editing and making it into a music video, and I am NOT making any monetary from these videos.  

The songs I used in the music video trailers can be found in iTunes.  My favorite movie and television drama genres are romance and romance-comedy including mythology, fantasy and WuXia martial arts.  

Don't be fooled by the ending in most of these music videos.  I only gave away the ending to an known or older movies and TV drama series.  So, let's put on the headset and watch these trailers with beautiful sentimental love songs. 

Enjoy!!!
